<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        /* General Reset and Body Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f7f7f7;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        header {
            background-color: #2d3b46;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        header nav a {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        header nav a:hover {
            background-color: #1a242f;
        }

        /* Main Content Styles */
        main {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff, #f1f1f1);
            padding: 40px 15px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 34px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .card-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            justify-items: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .card svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            fill: #007bff;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #777;
        }

        .card button {
            background: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }

        /* Footer Styles */
        footer {
            background-color: #2d3b46;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .card-container {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
                gap: 20px;
            }

            header .logo {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            header nav a {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">Sportopia</div>
        <div>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="#features">Features</a>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login">Login/Register</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>
</header>

<main>
    <h1 class="section-title">Plan and organize sports events with Sportopia</h1>
    <p class="section-title">Join today to create, schedule, and participate in sports events.</p>

    <section id="features">
        <h2 class="section-title">Key Features</h2>
        <div class="card-container">
            <div class="card">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3M16 7V3M3 8h18M4 12h16m-1 8h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5H9v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5m10 0h2"></path>
                </svg>
                <h3>Schedule Games</h3>
                <p>Effortlessly schedule upcoming games and events with our intuitive scheduling tools.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 20h10m-5-16a2 2 0 110 4 2 2 0 010-4zM4 15a4 4 0 014-4h8a4 4 0 014 4v1H4v-1z"></path>
                </svg>
                <h3>Manage Teams</h3>
                <p>Create and manage teams effortlessly, assign roles, and track team performance.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 17a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM6.343 9.657a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM15.657 9.657a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM6.343 14.343a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM15.657 14.343a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"></path>
                </svg>
                <h3>Track Statistics</h3>
                <p>Monitor detailed statistics and performance metrics for teams and individual players.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

